{"tid":1804460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【攬炒】12.31 攬炒跨年除夕夜行動  麻煩幫手推推PO (2)","createTime":"2019-12-31T04:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T08:34:22.000Z","uid":94771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d39f8c6c2d90b874395801e88d0a718f8c3a88","tid":1804460,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【攬炒行動】12.31 攬炒元旦  SUCK the EVE</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sdw4usb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdw4usb.jpg&h=437facb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGTnNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGTnNb.jpg&h=38237942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒數喎！<br />\n首先梗係要揀往年人流<span style=\"color: red;\">最集中</span>嘅地方聚咗人先：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海港城</span>、<span style=\"color: orange;\">圓方</span>、<span style=\"color: pink;\">時代廣場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之後再去特色景點進行倒數：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">維港兩岸</span>、<span style=\"color: violet;\">西九文化區</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">蘭桂芳</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXxbTUq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXxbTUq.png&h=9de06e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年雖然冇煙花<br />\n但有加強版 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「<span style=\"color: red;\">幻</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">彩</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">詠</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">香</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">江</span>」</span></strong><br />\n香港島多幢大廈樓頂將發放煙火<br />\n並在香港會議展覽中心外牆同時展示「2020」的字樣<br />\n照亮維多利亞港<br />\n伴你迎接精采新一年！<br />\n<br />\n咁精彩又點少得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白色煙霧</span></strong>作為元旦伴禮？<br />\n<br />\n今年係香港人不一樣的一年<br />\n我們渡過左不一樣的暑假<br />\n我們渡過左不一樣的聖誕<br />\n所以元旦亦唔會例外！<br />\n<br />\n我地要攬炒元旦<span style=\"color: red;\">喚醒</span>更多<span style=\"color: teal;\">置身事外</span>既香港人！<br />\n打破呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平行時空！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋在此號召各位元旦一齊出嚟！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今年倒數願望相信大家都一樣：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10！9！五！大！訴！求！缺！一！不！可！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7WzRHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7WzRHm.jpg&h=d0c7cd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同時大家唔好唔記得 「香港除夕倒數」大抽獎呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUAkNgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUAkNgf.jpg&h=ed9493c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知香港<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">平時啲network幾差架啦</span></strong><br />\n多少少人用都會<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">爆炸</span></span></strong><br />\n記得上去抽獎同玩遊戲呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n我地SUCK Channel為左呢半年既抗爭做左一條紀錄片<br />\n希望大家可以細心觀賞一下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DUJugrWyYc0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDUJugrWyYc0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=f62e3c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DUJugrWyYc0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家除夕見!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSUCK Channel : <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=b723bc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n#2 為 英文版文宣  <b